<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> حَجْبُ الحِرْمَانِ لَا يَدْخُلُ عَلَى:</span> الزَّوْجَيْنِ، وَالأَبَوَيْنِ، وَالوَلَدِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَسْقُطُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- الجَدُّ بِالأَبِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَكُلُّ جَدٍّ وَابْنٍ أَبْعَدَ بِأَقْرَبَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَكُلُّ جَدَّةٍ بِأُمٍّ، وَالقُرْبَى مِنْهُنَّ تَحْجُبُ البُعْدَى مُطْلَقاً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- لَا أَبٌ <span class="c2">(١)</span> أُمَّهُ، أَوْ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> أُمَّ أَبِيهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا يَرِثُ إِلَّا ثَلَاثٌ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> أُمُّ أُمٍّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَأُمُّ أَبٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَأُمُّ أَبِي أَبٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَإِنْ عَلَوْنَ أُمُومَةً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلِذَاتِ قَرَابَتَيْنِ مَعَ ذَاتِ قَرَابَةٍ:</span> ثُلُثَا السُّدُسِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (أ) و (ج): الأب.<br>(٢) في (أ): و.</p> </div>